}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== Features industrial-grade high-power 802.11n dual-band 3x3 mini-PCI with ESD protector, DNMA-H5 provides better-performance, reliability, and durability in the harshest temperature range of –40°C ~ +75°C.
The device uses the (industrial grade) AR9160-BC1B.
